1. *Jao* mi je što ne mogu da dođem na tvoj rođendan. (Oh, I'm sorry that I can't come to your birthday).

2. *Jao* šta je to bilo? (Oh, what was that?).

3. *Jao* pa to je velika greška. (Oh, that's a big mistake).

4. *Jao* kako ćemo sada da rešimo problem? (Oh, how are we going to solve the problem now?).

5. *Jao* pa nismo znali da je to bilo tako teško. (Oh, we didn't know it was so hard).